Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有答覆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:13.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往 要求展示歌與原始文明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.59,0:00:18.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並揚言自己不為所動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.73,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自從找回文化已過半世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:34.41,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這就是烙刻在傑特拉帝遺傳因子中的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:39.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也隱約感覺血脈賁張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:41.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最壞的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:45.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能需要動用艦炮連同基地付之一炬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:49.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有心理準備 奧格泰隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:54.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SK-4 空間跳躍成功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵達GalliaⅣ區域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河標準時間修正
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,+172.25
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是星球…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:15.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有天空…

Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:21.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}君は誰とキスをする
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:26.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}星を巡るよ 純情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:33.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}弱虫泣き虫連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:38.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}まだ行くんだと思う わたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:43.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}愛するより求めるより
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:52.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}疑うほうがずっとたやすい自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}痛いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}味方だけど愛してないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}守るけど側にいれないとか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:08.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}苦い二律背反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:13.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}今すぐ タッチミー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:18.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}運命ならばつながせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:24.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}君は誰とキスをする
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:29.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}わたし それともあの娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:34.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}こころ揺らす言葉より
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:40.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)}無責任に抱いて 限界

Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:21.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}你願為誰獻上誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:26.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}任這純情環遊星海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:33.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}背負著愛哭跟軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:38.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}認為仍能前進的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:43.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}對比起去愛與尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.18,0:01:52.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}更容易去懷疑人的自己感到惱火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:55.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}是朋友卻無法去愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}想守護卻無法在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:08.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}令人痛苦的二律背反
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:13.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}現在 立刻 Touch me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:18.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}若是命運便任其相連
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:24.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}你願為誰獻上誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.51,0:02:29.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}是我 還是那個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:34.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}比起讓心動搖的言語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.06,0:02:40.17,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)}你無責任的擁抱已經是極限

Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:53.05,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(400,440)\pos(455,578)\shad0\bord2}Fastest Delivery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是後天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花的首演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:57.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就沒話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近無精打采啊 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:05.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.93,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐和早乙女一直請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過後天就能見到蘭花了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:19.68,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人說小別勝新婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:23.11,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 謝謝路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.18,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我還是繼續休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:31.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.15,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是首演前好好放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:37.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難過 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將開始降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.53,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大氣層的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:40.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是SMS骷髏小隊 亞爾特·早乙女准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任雪露·諾姆護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:44.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表示感謝 亞爾特准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:49.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第33海軍陸戰隊隊長 奧格泰少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.47,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遠萬里趕來辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他們也該安分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體傑特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.10,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向銀河的精靈 雪露·諾姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.24,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:23.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:29.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:42.05,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.13,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願為傑特拉帝人唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:48.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:49.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談判破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:10.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還有身為人質的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會因為違反生態保障法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被強制社區勞動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.06,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是它那麼溫順
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:41.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是它安慰了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給亞爾特送生日禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤單一人時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:51.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時一起接受處罰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.81,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是稀有品種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:09.64,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致查了生態地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒登載
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:22.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.75,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傑特拉帝人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:29.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 請注意措辭為好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.09,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Gallia4進行空間跳躍通信的時間延遲是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為設置有中繼點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縮短為127分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受斷層影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.45,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在趕去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七天後才能抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時已經塵埃落定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:55.99,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.25,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.39,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發起暴動的一派
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制了幾乎所有Queadluun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.46,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(785,655)}倍力服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.60,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求交出艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就威脅取雪露·諾姆以下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.29,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰問團一行人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:09.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽大妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.76,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 明明預感到不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.30,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該讓他獨自去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:23.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕從要求慰問演出開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有計劃性的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:30.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 行事如此巧妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.61,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:32.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧他們說得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露因病無法演出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.92,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然成了導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無非是需要口實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:48.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:52.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇爾 不能去救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.51,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾特應付不過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:57.31,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.72,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠水救不了近火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:00.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.54,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒能把禮物給亞爾特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.78,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼都沒能說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:13.79,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:19.03,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許有一個方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:40.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 出發前幾天身體不適
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬是不聽勸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:46.94,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持健康不也是工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:56.40,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無話說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.33,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.88,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是靠唱歌能挽回的形勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.95,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過送禮物…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.67,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你去天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:22.17,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲 你看住這傻瓜別胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:23.74,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:31.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會受斷層影響的新型空間跳躍引擎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:36.21,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 特別借來了LAI開發中的部件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.80,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說實用還問題多多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但客觀時間與主觀時間毫無誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.43,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果得以實用化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河將縮小到現在的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.97,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 十分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:54.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家在開發這麼可怕的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.27,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請千萬小心用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:59.38,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦
